{
  "2343920": {
    "name": "特快小火车 Trackline Express",
    "steam_appid": 2343920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/03b7d38cf773922f49981f75391c57ca.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>全体上车！</strong><br>即购买车票，登上特快小火车！免责声明：可能有部分铁轨缺失。偶尔还有野蛮人的袭击。不过无需担心，我们的火车是最可靠的。有些只需要稍微时不时升级一下。除此之外，等待你的将是一段完美的旅程！<br>我们有没有提到野火？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/dd3d71df3175fc39e7e488c5bcf7d141.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/dd3d71df3175fc39e7e488c5bcf7d141.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/dd3d71df3175fc39e7e488c5bcf7d141.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《特快小火车》是一款火车建造游戏，你需要在保证乘客安全的前提下到达各个车站，避免受到攻击和野火的侵袭。收集木材、岩石、矿石和煤炭，然后将它们转化为各种资源，使用途中解锁的蓝图创建新的建筑和设备。<br><br>游戏融合了各种独特的游戏元素，既能吸引喜欢策略和资源管理的玩家，也能吸引寻求更轻松惬意，但偶尔有些刺激转折的游戏体验的人。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/add2e7ea3cec5a96bf85970a8b0a14f4.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>收集资源</strong><br>沙漠中的资源并不多，因此你必须考虑如何以最佳方式利用它们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/c0c2a4fb44e01a98cb2c6dd720d903c9.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/c0c2a4fb44e01a98cb2c6dd720d903c9.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/c0c2a4fb44e01a98cb2c6dd720d903c9.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/a82ff4ebd4114ee09f4819d761dc2be6.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>解锁蓝图</strong><br>你需要收集足够的金币来解锁蓝图，才能建造任何东西。蓝图一旦解锁，就可以自由使用。金币非常稀有，所以要善加利用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/96aed2107f864aba7380ec3b1090aac8.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/96aed2107f864aba7380ec3b1090aac8.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/96aed2107f864aba7380ec3b1090aac8.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/9eaa1e1566d3da634da3523a6bfdbd1e.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>进行建设</strong><br>只要有足够的资源和正确的蓝图，就可以创建多个建筑和设备，帮助你继续前进和生存。你首先要建造什么？获取煤炭供火车使用的矿场？或者为你的水箱打一口井？还是要选择装备，以抵御即将到来的威胁……每次游戏都不一样，可能需要安排不同的优先级。关键是适应。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/521d48423865ca76aa8db62cc8557946.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/521d48423865ca76aa8db62cc8557946.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/521d48423865ca76aa8db62cc8557946.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/7c9cce2fa4e0817853c032bc7af358bf.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>保护你的乘客</strong><br>袭击频繁发生。你必须奋力保护你的车队。还好你有一些物品可以使用。随着越来越多的乘客到来，你必须更有创意地使用它们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/90b0158154059c267196fe22671e0f23.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/90b0158154059c267196fe22671e0f23.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/90b0158154059c267196fe22671e0f23.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/aae6358dbd993936f2d25610a925154e.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>让火车不断前进</strong><br>给火车加煤，建造新的车厢和新的设备，以抵御基本上所有的危险。随着游戏的进行，时间和距离的增加，游戏会越来越难，因此请尽量安排自动化运行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/5ed5d1ca61a89bbc1982a238afb8211a.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/5ed5d1ca61a89bbc1982a238afb8211a.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/5ed5d1ca61a89bbc1982a238afb8211a.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/b317fa1e661a6321a2e5a7def0123382.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>与朋友一起游戏</strong><br>带你的朋友一起搭火车！通过《特快小火车》多人模式，在通往最终目的地的旅途中携手应对挑战。联合你们的力量，战略性地规划下一步，打败即将到来的威胁！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/78fec37919d3d3b64b2db0e5c7ed8257.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/78fec37919d3d3b64b2db0e5c7ed8257.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/78fec37919d3d3b64b2db0e5c7ed8257.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/2286b4794a3ad2f2a9d2a161b7882d29.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>每日挑战模式</strong><br>你玩游戏的时间很零碎吗？别担心！这款游戏有「每日挑战」模式。每天都有全新的随机生成地图供大家畅玩，让你和你的好友能够挑战自我！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/57e17a730e214f60282940d92b834b0e.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/57e17a730e214f60282940d92b834b0e.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/57e17a730e214f60282940d92b834b0e.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/ac105a108b2a0b3b82d75bd6501ec2f4.avif?t=1746614149\" width=614 height=110 /></span><br><strong>游戏特色</strong><br>- 重玩性高<br>- 许多物品可供收集和制作<br>- 多种游戏模式<br>- 在线和本地（局域网）多人游戏模式（实验功能）<br>- 迷你任务等你完成<br>- 随机决定的地图生成器<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/f222c10641427657057abdc567c17522.poster.avif?t=1746614149\" width=610 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/f222c10641427657057abdc567c17522.webm?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343920/extras/f222c10641427657057abdc567c17522.mp4?t=1746614149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
